from [here](https://developer.apple.com/library/mac/documentation/graphicsimaging/reference/Quartz_Services_Ref/DeprecationAppendix/AppendixADeprecatedAPI.html) seems that there's no replacement for `CGDisplayIOServicePort`
for `SetFrontProcess` there's [this](http://stackoverflow.com/a/2334362) answer from SO that should do the work:

``` objective-c
NSRunningApplication* app = [NSRunningApplication runningApplicationWithProcessIdentifier: PID];
[app activateWithOptions: NSApplicationActivateAllWindows];
```
